  "title": "Enforcement Officer X 5 (Training Provided | Islandwide)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li><strong>Island wide, Singapore</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Salary: $2,700 to $3,300 + Allowances</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Bonus: $3,500</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Training Provided</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Patrolling and conducting enforcement duties related to illegal parking and public health.</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Attending to public feedback and concerns.</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Check parking / summon.</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Able to commit to a 12-hours duty schedule.</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Possess Class 2B motorcycle licence.</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now button</strong> with the following information in the resume</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li>\n  <li>Current and Expected salary</li>\n  <li>Reason for leaving</li>\n  <li>Date of availability</li>\n  <li>Education background</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>LIONG ZHAO GUAN (R22107632)</p>\n<p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
